<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="though-conj">though <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ðəʊ/    美 /ðoʊ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-although">1.★ <strong>虽然 (although)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Though I need money for myself, I’m still willing to help. 
虽然我自己也需要钱，但我还是乐意帮忙。</p><footer>外研③ – 2</footer></div>

<p>注: though意为“虽然”，引导状语从句时，可将从句中的表语、状语等提前，其他成分保持陈述语序。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Much though I admire her, I cannot excuse her faults. 
虽然我非常崇拜她，但我不能原谅她的错误。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>即使：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Though I fail, I shall try again. 
即使失败，我也要再试一次。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>可是；不过；然而：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’ll probably say no, though it’s worth asking. 
他很可能会拒绝，不过问一下也没什么坏处。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Though not very big, but the restaurant is popular in our area.  （2016 全国 改错）  </li>
<li>If scientists have learned a lot about the universe, there is much we still don’t know. 
  （2015安徽改 改错）  </li>
<li>Unsatisfied <strong><em>_</em></strong>__ with the payment, he took the job just to get some work experience.  （2009 重庆）<br />
A.though was he<br />
B.though he was<br />
C.he was though<br />
D.was he though  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. 去掉but  2. If → Though / Although  3. B  </p></div>